---
title: Mediterranean Falafel, Bacon & Feta Sub with Cucumber, Capsicum Relish & Aioli
description: Pack in the flavours of the Mediterranean into a toasted panini sub so you can get a taste of everything all at once! We’re adding
falafels with chargrilled capsicum relish and creamy feta crumbled over. The garlic aioli is a must for fragrance and finishing with a side of fries, you can never go wrong.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66c6abebb372008c572c36b2-35881e4a.jpeg
